Book one of The Stormlight Archive
Follows a dude named Kaladin who goes from being a surgeon's assistant to a slave to worse than a slave.  He finds out he's awesome and kicks some major butt.  
Also follows a dude name Dalinar who's the king's right hand man.  He starts going crazy when it rains.
Also follows a chick named Shallan who draws stuff and tries to steal something from the king's sister.